channel.title: Server trouble
channel.description:
OK, I advertised my server on codefasga, shut it down for a day because of this noob using SYIPKPKER. Now when I try to add it back to code fasga, it wont work, it says Please correct these errors:
* The server could not be contacted
So I was like.... WTF. So I tried to add it to moparscape server status, and it still says it can not be contacted. So I thought the SYIPKPKER noob fu_ked my server up, so I used my old one, and it still says
Please correct these errors:
* The server could not be contacted So something on my computer got messed up I guess? Anyone have any ideas what?
